A responsive, multi-page portfolio website built with HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript to showcase professional skills, projects, and contact information.

## ðŸ“‹ Project Overview

This project is a complete portfolio website designed for web developers or designers to present their work professionally. It features a clean, modern design with smooth transitions and full responsiveness across all device sizes.

